This is a simple project that allows the user to switch between Light Mode and Dark Mode using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Features:-
    -> Light and Dark theme switch
    -> Smooth transition between themes
    -> Uses HTML, CSS, and JavaScript only

How to Use:-
    -> Open the project in your browser
    -> Click the toggle button to switch between Light and Dark mode

Files:-
    -> index.html – Structure of the webpage
    -> style.css – Styles for light and dark themes
    ->script.js – Handles the toggle functionality
